Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橋田 至(はしだいたる)）\Nじゃあ クラッキング始めるお
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start the cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
