Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橋田）お？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）中止だ
