Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:30.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）岡部は？\N（橋田）不明　僕 忙しかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では まゆ氏 御武運を！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（椎名(しいな)まゆり）ダル君も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橋田）うむ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コミマ 今日が最終日だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is today the last day of Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 紅莉栖ちゃんも来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have lots of cute {cosplay}costumes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カワイイコスプレの子とか\Nいっぱいいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:46.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べ… 別に興味とかないし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not really interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:48.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Okarin's up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン どうしたのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあね クラッキングを\N中止するって言ったきり…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we weren't doing the cracking, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりなんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's gonna reach a high of 35°C !{35°C - 95°F}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）最高気温 35度だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying hydrated is the best way to prevent heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱中症防止には―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水分をこまめにとるのが\N大切なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to Comima today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\N今日も… コミマじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）\Nうん　これから行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:17.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\Nそうか… 気をつけてな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）お…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外 日ざし強いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really sunny out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあね トゥットゥルー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:29.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）まゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:30.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）おっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）８月17日\NＤメールを消すたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each D-mail I undid delayed Mayuri's death by one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりの死は\N１日ずつズレていった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:46.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めは13日に訪れていたものが―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erasing Suzuha's D-mail made the events of the 13th occur on the 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈴羽(すずは)のメールを\N消すことによって14日…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feyris, Rukako, Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:53.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フェイリス るか子 萌郁(もえか)…\Nそのたびに―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If each one pushed it back a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日ずつ延びたとすると―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:02:00.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界線で\Nまゆりの死が訪れるのは 17日…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then in this world line, Mayuri will die on the 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, before 8:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日の夜８時前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでに…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）\Nオカリーン　ハア ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハアーッ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）探していたのは\N見つかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:13.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しで売り切れちゃう\Nところだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダル君の分も確保したし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I got one for Daru too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there was a book on a robot anime I thought you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… オカリンの好きそうな\Nロボットアニメの本もあったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってみる？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 俺はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？\Nせっかく来たのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\N少し考えたいことがあってな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if there's anywhere you'd like to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこか見に行きたい所があったら\N言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？ もう帰る？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:41.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… あっ\N何を言っている？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to think about, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考え事というのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the Organization assassins hiding in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この会場に潜んでいる\N機関の刺客のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do something to escape their clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつらをなんとかして\N出し抜かねばならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not careful, they might find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘタに動くと\N感づかれる可能性がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夕方まで\N予定どおりに行動するのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the original plan until evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any bad people like that are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな悪い人は\Nいないと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）偵察に行ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet back here at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１５２０(いちごうふたまる)にここで落ち合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）いいな\N（まゆり）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリーン\Nジュース 向こうで売ってるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're selling juice over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）あと５時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あきらめるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before then, I'll have to find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでに見つけるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a way for her to survive without changing world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界線を変えずに―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが生き残る方法を
