Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:29.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）はあ？ どうして私が\N橋田に協力しなきゃいけないの…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to help you, Hashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノート？ サークル一覧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A list of circles at Comima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないわよ そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラック？ ２段目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？ ２段目はダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at the second shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア… リアルに訴えるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously having you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーん… 何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングは\Nどうなっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）\Nあんたが中止って言うから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so we haven't touched it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,丸３日 ほったらかしのままよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what's going on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげん 説明しろ\Nいったい何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが… 今日 死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri will die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）聞いたわ 前に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからクラッキングが\N必要なんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you're doing the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To erase the first D-mail you sent—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部が最初に送った\NＤメールを消せば…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ダメだ\Nクラッキングはなしだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think of a way to save Mayuri without the cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラッキングをしないで―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりを助ける方法を考える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:22.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしなければならない\N事情が生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）どういう事情よ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）今は説明できない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別の方法が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）別の方法って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）頼む！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）説明して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I won't be able to think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃないと…\N方法も考えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,協力も… できない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running out of time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）時間がないんでしょ\N隠してる場合じゃない　岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hide things now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:49.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ウハ～\Nやっと帰ってこれた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ オカリンはラボ寄ってく？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want to stop by the lab, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was thinking of getting some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは ごはん\N食べていこうかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン？ 疲れちゃった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ん？ あっ いや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）もうすぐ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}almost time for her to die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりは また…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that never works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げても結局…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）オカリン？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ねえ オカリン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は なんで\Nついてきてくれたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely went to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 どこもあんまり\N見ないままだったし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to check something out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たいものとかあったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've shown you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうちょっと\N案内してあげられたのになあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many things Mayushii knows more than Okarin about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンより詳しいことって\Nほとんどないから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日はね ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never gone to Comima together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンとコミマ行くの\N初めてだから―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii was happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは うれしかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）まゆり…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,るか子が―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see Rukako looking embarrassed in his costume!{cosplay}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コスプレして\N恥ずかしがっているところを―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てやろうかと思ったのだが―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来ていなくて残念だった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）そうだね　来てたら\N絶対 人気出るのになあ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if he had, he would've been really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Ruka would've gotten his photo on all the blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして るか君は\Nいろんなブログに―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,画像をアップされまくって―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワールドワイドな\Nスーパースターになるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and he would've become a worldwide superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを見て まゆしぃは―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Mayushii would've seen it and said, "He's come a long way."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:39.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠い所に行っちゃったなあと\N思いをはせるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）アハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当になりそうだから困る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could really see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次はオカリンも\Nコスプレしてくれると―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be even better if Okarin wore a costume{cosplayed} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとうれしいかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）考えておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）その代わり まゆりも\Nコスプレして参加するのだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, you'd have to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. We'll call Rukako and Christina,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな だとしたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,るか子にクリスティーナも呼ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N２人がコスプレするように―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can convince them to do it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが説得するのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが出来たら真打ちとして―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do that, then I,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この狂気の\Nマッドサイエンティスト―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma the mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳳凰院凶真(ほうおういんきょうま)が\Nコミマに降臨しようではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,shall make my {cosplay}costuming debut at Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　道は険しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kurisu was interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 紅莉栖ちゃんは\N脈ありだったし―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃ 次のコミマまでに\N頑張ってみるね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so Mayushii will try her best to do it by the next Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The next—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? My watch isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃの懐中\N止まっちゃってる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おかしいな\Nさっき… うわあっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ヤダ もうヤダ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来たのに\Nどうして まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）オカリン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ここで じっとしていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）変えてやる 運命を…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）因果を自分の手で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll stop it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I let that car hit me... If I die here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がここで はねられれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命を投げ出せば―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが変わるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}something has to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）オカリン！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）オカ… リン？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へへッ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと… やっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Finally, I was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役に立った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii was useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンの―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,役に… 立てたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リン…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,の…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ まゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see the stars from here, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからじゃ あんまり―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,星 見えないな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの… あんまりだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.23,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz340\move(1075.33,501,928.666,501,0,2446)}I want to talk to you. \NKurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（橋田）じゃあ\Nクラッキング始めるお
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start the cracking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）岡部？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）あっ\N（橋田）おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）いつまで\Nそこにいるつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\N一人にさせてくれと\N言ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've been on the roof for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 屋上に\N上がったまま―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,without so much as a peep, so I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:07.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何時間も物音ひとつ\N立てずにいたら心配する…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not worried, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… いや しないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop the cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして\Nクラッキングをやめるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）お前だって\Nよくないと言ったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought the FBI would come, and you got scared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タイーホフラグが立って\Nビビったんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）順法精神に\N目覚めたと言ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to be thought of as a law-abiding citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,らしくないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your normal hotshot attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもの独善的な態度は\Nどこへいったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The great mad scientist, Hououin Kyouma—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気のマッドサイエン…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\N独善的でなんかいられるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I act like that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気のマッドサイエンティスト？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳳凰院凶真？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの全部 妄想だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,設定だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かなかったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew within five seconds of meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初対面で気付いてましたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you time leap again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）まさか また\Nタイムリープしてきたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've helped you with everything so far, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さんざん\N相談に乗ってやったでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまさら遠慮するな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it this far by thinking things through together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までも２人で考えて\Nここまで きたんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）“ここまできた”か…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha and Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鈴羽やフェイリス　るか子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukako...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To come this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの思いを犠牲にして\Nやっとたどりついた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I sacrificed the things they loved the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, this is how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:22.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが こんな結末なのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe, you were crying back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）ねえ 岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき泣いてたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋田も心配してた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida was worried too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought maybe you had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖い夢でも\N見たんじゃないかって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:51.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部の力になりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,July 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）７月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri and I went to Dr. Nakabachi's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は まゆりと\N中鉢(なかばち)博士の会見に出かけた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I saw Makise Kurisu collapsed after being stabbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで俺は―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者かに刺され倒れている\N牧瀬紅莉栖を発見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know by whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a text to Daru's cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電話レンジにつながっていた\Nダルの携帯にメールを送った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which was connected to the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The first D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１通目のＤメール
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the message that moved us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ベータ世界線から―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from the beta world line to the alpha world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルファ世界線に\N移動することになった元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Deleting that message from SERN's database
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＳＥＲＮ(セルン)に捉えられた\Nそのメールを消し―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and returning to the beta world line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ベータ世界線に\N戻るということは―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,means going back to that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり その世界に戻るということ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）ハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\Nベータ世界線に戻れば―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If we return to the beta world line...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we undo that first D-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのＤメールを消せば―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）出てあげなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）出てあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:08.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）まゆりか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あっ うん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daru told me you were acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あのね\Nダル君から聞いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリン 何か変だったって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）別に何もない\Nダルの勘違いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii's been so busy with Comima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃ\Nコミマに夢中で―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンのこと\N見てあげられなかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that she couldn't spend time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you used to talk to Mayushii about all kinds of stuff, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あのね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昔よく まゆしぃに\Nいろんなお話してくれたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There were four Organization generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,機関には幹部が４人いて―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Geppu, Sudachi, Seiyuu, and Jakkou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲップとスダチと\N声優とじゃこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbu, Suzaku, Seiryuu, and Byakko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）玄武(げんぶ)と朱雀(すざく)と\N青龍(せいりゅう)と白虎(びゃっこ)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あ… そうそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:49.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうね オカリンの話\Nとっても面白かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked hearing about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃのこと\N重荷に感じたら言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii is ever a burden, you'd tell me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you alone for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ とりあえず切るね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし まゆしぃに\Nお話できることがあったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mayushii can do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,call me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも電話してね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）まゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:07.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紅莉栖）すぐに行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From your voice, I can guess what she was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,岡部の声 聞いてたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆりが何言ってたか\N大体 分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go see her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに会いに行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のことは―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to come up with any answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ここで話してても\N何も答えは出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you stay here to talk to with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you were sitting here alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:22.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから あんたは\N今まで 一人で悩んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, you should go see Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら\Nまゆりに会いに行くべきよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll only hurt my pride if you stay here and worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで ただ\Nあんたに心配されても―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のプライドが傷つくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:32.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先 行くわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:33.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mayushii. I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）まゆしぃです\N今 電話に出られません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One of {cosplayers}them said Mayushii left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり まゆ氏\Nかなり前に帰ったって―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コスプレの子が言ってたお
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you since it's Obon, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お盆だから おばあちゃん\N会いに来てくれたんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been having scary dreams lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのね…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 怖い夢ばっかり見るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dreams, terrible things happen to Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢の中でね―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも まゆしぃは\Nひどい目に遭うの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets shot with a pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピストルで\Nパーンって撃たれたり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or she's in a car accident or run over by a train,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,車の事故に巻き込まれたり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電車にひかれたり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything seems like it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで本当のことみたいで―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary, and it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:50.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっごく怖くて痛くて\N悲しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to scream for help as loud as I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“誰か助けて”って―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生懸命\N声 出すんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出せなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして\Nそんな夢 見るのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of the dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…でね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その夢の最後には―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin always comes to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもオカリンが\N助けに来てくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii says, "Thank you, Okarin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“オカリンありがとう”って\N言うんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その声もオカリンには\N聞こえなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃのこと抱きしめて―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He holds Mayushii, and he looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっても悲しそうな顔をして―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He never cries, but you can tell he really wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 泣かないんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生懸命\N我慢してるのが分かるの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mayushii says, "I'm sorry," but he doesn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから まゆしぃも―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〝ごめんね〞って\N言うんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,声は やっぱり届かなくて\N目が覚めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね\N楽しい話するね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk about something fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, there have been a lot of new lab members!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近 ラボメンが\Nすごく増えたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖ちゃんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Kurisu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Moeka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,萌郁さん るか君に\Nフェリスちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka, and Feyris!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと鈴(すず)さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初は２人だけだったのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu is super smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紅莉栖ちゃんなんか\Nすっごい頭よくって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and she talks about all these really hard things with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンと難しい話なんか\Nいっぱいしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,にぎやかで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin looks happy now that he gets to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:06.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンも\Nたくさん話せて楽しそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, sometimes I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまには思い出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）最初に まゆしぃが\Nラボに押しかけたころのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time Mayushii went to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the beginning of spring, but it was snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,春先なのに\N珍しく雪が降ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the lab after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:27.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校が終わってラボに行くとね\Nオカリンはいないの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:30.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でね お部屋の片づけしたり\Nしてるうちに―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was cleaning up the room, he came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンが来てね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, "Welcome back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“おかえり”って言うと―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't say, "I'm back."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ただいま”とは言わなくて―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Good work."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ご苦労”って答えて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:43.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのあとは\N毎日２時間ぐらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, every day after that, I'd go there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for about two hours, and we would barely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんど お話もしないで\N過ごしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't bad. We were simply there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤな沈黙とかじゃなくて―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ そこにいるって感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passed so slowly, and it was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり ゆっくり\N優しい時間が流れてて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii thought she really was like a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃは本当に\N人質みたいだなあって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）\N何かいいことでもあったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing good happened, but it was good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいことはなかったけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:09.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）そうか\N幻想を見たのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. You saw some kind of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be an attack by Organization General Illusion Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,機関の幹部―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イリュージョンコンダクターからの\N攻撃の可能性がある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）そっか\Nじゃあ 気をつけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll have to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I bet that Illusion Contactor—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そのイリュージョン\N子だくさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）コンダクターだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あ… うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think he's a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人は 多分\N悪い人じゃないと思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I haven't spent much time talking with Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近ね\Nオカリンとお話しする時間―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと減っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:39.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前は オカリンの顔を見れば―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be that, when I saw him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell what he was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何 考えてるか\N分かったんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近は\N分からなくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:47.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell he's really suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:50.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か とってもつらそうで―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しそうで―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like he's always about to cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもいつも\N泣きだしそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know he's thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは まゆしぃの\Nことなんだって分かって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンの重荷には\Nなりたくないのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a burden to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was talking about something sad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか また\N悲しい話になっちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まゆしぃ ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Mayushii's been lonely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さみしくなっちゃったの\Nかもしれないね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おばあちゃん…\Nいつまでも このままじゃ―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, I can't stay this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いられないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）このままでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）オ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オカリンだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして\Nここが分かったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always know where my hostage is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）人質がどこにいるのか\N俺は常に把握しているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから お前は\N俺の手から逃れられん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対にだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）あんまり\N無理しちゃダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Hououin Kyouma,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:56.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に心配されるほど\Nこの鳳凰院凶真は やわではない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,am not so weak that I need you to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話せるときがきたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを話す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）帰るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）ああ！\Nでも その前に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（岡部）分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get another Upa toy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーぱのガチャガチャ\Nやっていくんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（まゆり）エヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～
